handling, sale, or use of any quantity of explosive, explosive material, fireworks, or pyrotechnic special effects within the scope of chapter 56.
Exception: Storage in Group R-3 occupancies of smokeless propellant, black powder, and small arms primers for personal use, not for resale and in accordance with section 5606.
105.6.8 Hazardous materials. An operational permit is required to store, transport on site, dispense, use or handle hazardous materials in excess of the amounts listed in Table 105.6.8.
